                   <h4>Legal Protection</h4>
                    <p>Copyright registration serves as prima facie evidence in the court of law over ownership of the work. Therefore, copyright registration gives the owner legal protection for his/her work.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 agile_services_grid">
                    <div class="agileits_w3layouts_service_grid">
                        <div class="w3_agileits_service_grid">
                            <span></span>
