                        </div>
                    </div>
                     <h4>Branding or Goodwill</h4>
                    <p>Registered copyright can be used for marketing and creating a sense of goodwill and quality in the minds of your customer. Registered copyright show others that you care about your work.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 agile_services_grid">
                    <div class="agileits_w3layouts_service_grid">
                        <div class="w3_agileits_service_grid">
                            <span></span>
                            <i class="fa fa-bullhorn" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                   <h4>Global Protection</h4>
                    <p>Works that are copyrighted in many other countries are accorded similar privileges here in India. Likewise, works copyright registered in India are accorded protection in many foreign countries.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-3 agile_services_grid">
                    <div class="agileits_w3layouts_service_grid">
                        <div class="w3_agileits_service_grid">
                            <span></span>
                            <i class="fa fa-building-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                     <h4>Restricts Unauthorized Reproduction</h4>
                    <p>Copyright registration will establish that you are serious about copyright infringement. This will help impede unauthorized reproduction of the work as it provides the owner with a host of legal remedies.</p>
